the kid I'm trying to adopt.

24
00:00:58,417 --> 00:01:00,375
I mean, I don't get it,
but I'm sure

25
00:01:00,417 --> 00:01:03,083
she's more evolved
than I am.

26
00:01:03,125 --> 00:01:05,166
I don't want
to fight anymore.

27
00:01:05,208 --> 00:01:08,458
We're not fighting.
We're... disagreeing.

28
